abstract: Marten Mickos has opted to run another high-flier in the open-source software world.
snippet: Marten Mickos has opted to run another high-flier in the open-source software world.
lead_paragraph: Marten Mickos, the former chief executive of MySQL, will soon be named the chief executive of Eucalyptus, another open-source software maker.

headline.main: Former MySQL Chief Lands at Eucalyptus
